message: Let's split it 50/50, a fair start!
You started high, I'll meet you in the middle
I'll meet you halfway, but not all the way down
You're going down, I'm going up!
You're pushing me down, but I'll still meet you halfway
You're getting squeezed, I'm getting richer!
You're getting too greedy, I'll try to squeeze you back
You're getting desperate, I'm getting bold!
You're getting too confident, I'll try to take back control
You're running out of time, I'm running out of patience!
You're getting desperate, I'll try to squeeze one last deal out of you
Last chance, take it or leave it!
